snippet.title: Scarlett Johansson & Disney Settle Explosive ‘Black Widow’ Lawsuit I THR News
snippet.description:
The settlement ends a back-and-forth PR battle pitting the CAA-repped star against the studio that was poised to have dramatic implications for all of Hollywood’s majors.
To learn more about this story:

https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/scarlett-johansson-disney-settle-black-widow-lawsuit-1235022598/
